{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df73222025","title":"给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d76b328746","index":0,"year":1955,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"df73222025"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"206c86b5b6","type":"title","text":"给周世钟的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"},{"id":"1f0190d85c","type":"paragraph","text":"停元兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"},{"id":"30a4f03963","type":"paragraph","text":"你的信好久就收到了，你的大作及附件各种都已读悉，极为感谢！喝写的字至今未能应命。你那里还不那样急需吧，我想等一等再讲，如何？你下去跑没有？最好一年下去跑几次，每次两三星期也好。我最近出外跑了一次，觉头脑清新得多。你下去时，不只看学校，还可看些别的东西。再谈。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"},{"id":"b1e5a0ed10","type":"paragraph","text":"顺问教安","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"},{"id":"af12411335","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"},{"id":"355d268e46","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年十一月二十四日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"},{"id":"78687cb5de","type":"paragraph","text":"口1]周世钊，字婷元，当时任湖南省教育厅副厅长兼湖南省第一师范学校校长。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025"}],"page":{"id":"8b62a6c6bb","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"df73222025","start":76,"end":76}}}},"__N_SSG":true}